Package uw.rfpk.mda.nonmem

Class Summary
JobInfo Job information dialog.
Likelihood This class handles likelihood evaluation method.
MDA This is the main class of the Model Design Agent application.
MDAFrame This class creates a window for the model design agent., There are eleven buttons, a menu bar and a text area in the window.
Output This class defines an object that contains output data.
ParameterAll This class handels the parameter estimates in all the sub-problems of a job.
Utility This class defines static functions used by steps.
XMLReader This class defines an object that reads two XML documents: Spk source file and Spk report file.
XMLWriter This class defines an object that generates an XML SPK input file.
